s/%e8%a7%80%e9%bb%9e/article/20200424/s00012/1587668223335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a7%2580%25e9%25bb%259e%2Farticle%2F20200424%2Fs00012%2F1587668223335&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCSyWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=a96c1396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a7%2580%25e9%25bb%259e%2Farticle%2F20200424%2Fs00012%2F1587668223335&h=6d9eac90\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a7%80%e9%bb%9e/article/20200424/s00012/1587668223335</a>"},{"pid":"14128ab5fb0f1f05acb462704046cbfc457cee00","tid":2370584,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2a0ab8f1d866c682718c4a4c542649590aafc47","tid":2370584,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c038c5b2d294b75719369ba43a5820dccc2e283a","tid":2370584,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08a1477636f5563e80f28fe5d4fd2ef44830cd98","tid":2370584,"uid":362827,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"想塑造佢好打得，下任特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:09:32.000Z","msg":"邊輪到佢呀 佢之前比人調唔係因為太廢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩都比哂佢做 有咩鑊咪佢食哂囉 佢嗰啲job全部都吃力不討好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"係喎 差d唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報文章】國務院周三公布特區政府5名局長新任命，其中較受政圈關注的，是原入境處長曾國衞出任政制及內地事務局長，聶德權則調任公務員事務局長。綜合政圈消息，特首林鄭月娥不下一次向中央提出換閣，今次突然獲批，組合卻非完全是林鄭所想，據聞林鄭向中央提出換班的名單中，原本不涉聶德權。政圈及官場都估計，今次觸發中央開綠燈同意換人，<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"purple\">是因中央要將聶德權從政制局調走，其中一說是建制陣營對聶德權不滿聲甚高，甚至他要為區選大敗負責。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a7%80%e9%bb%9e/article/20200424/s00012/1587668223335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a7%2580%25e9%25bb%259e%2F